⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Question 93/120 – Merge Source & Target

🎤 Interview Question

You have:

Source

emp_id	name	salary

101	John	65000
102	Alice	50000
104	Bob	70000


Target

emp_id	name	salary

101	John	60000
102	Alice	50000
103	David	45000


Write PySpark code to:

Insert new employees.

Update existing employees if salary changes.



---

✅ Recommended Solution

from delta.tables import DeltaTable

target = DeltaTable.forPath(spark, "/target/employees")

(
    target.alias("t")
    .merge(
        source_df.alias("s"),
        "t.emp_id = s.emp_id"
    )
    .whenMatchedUpdate(
        condition="t.salary <> s.salary",
        set={
            "salary": "s.salary"
        }
    )
    .whenNotMatchedInsertAll()
    .execute()
)


---

