⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Question 94/120 – Find Missing Records

🎤 Interview Question

Find employees present in the source but missing from the target.


---

📊 Source

emp_id

101
102
103
104



---

📊 Target

emp_id

101
103



---

✅ Expected Output

emp_id

102
104



---

✅ Recommended Solution

missing_df = source_df.join(
    target_df,
    "emp_id",
    "left_anti"
)

missing_df.show()


---

🎤 Most Asked Interview Questions

Q1. Which join is used?

Answer

left_anti


---

Q2. Why not use an Inner Join?

Answer

Inner Join returns matching records, whereas Left Anti returns only records missing from the target.


